to music.

06:19.462 --> 06:21.756
Oh, my God, who am I?

06:23.341 --> 06:25.594
-Renfield?
-Hmm?

06:26.595 --> 06:29.848
Sorry, no, I swallowed a bug.

06:31.057 --> 06:32.892
Unintentionally.

06:32.892 --> 06:34.436
What-what other way
is there to...

06:34.436 --> 06:36.021
Would you like
to share your story?

06:36.980 --> 06:39.899
No. Thank-thank you.
I don't think you'd understand.

06:39.899 --> 06:42.652
I know it's scary.

06:42.652 --> 06:45.947
And you think things
are never gonna change,

06:45.947 --> 06:48.325
but I promise you,
one day you're gonna realize

06:48.325 --> 06:50.577
that you can have
the life that you want.

06:53.371 --> 06:55.123
But in the meantime, I just hope

06:55.123 --> 06:57.792
that you get something
out of coming here.

07:01.254 --> 07:02.964
I am.

07:02.964 --> 07:04.924
That's great.

07:04.924 --> 07:07.135
Oh, yes, I'm getting something

07:07.135 --> 07:09.387
out of coming here: victims.

07:09.387 --> 07:10.889
But not these victims.

07:10.889 --> 07:12.557
Let's do our affirmations.

07:14.100 --> 07:17.395
I am enough, and I have enough.

07:17.395 --> 07:19.522
I deserve happiness.

07:19.522 --> 07:21.733
I am grateful for all that I am,

07:21.733 --> 07:24.527
and I take full charge
of my life today.

07:24.527 --> 07:26.029
They can repeat these

07:26.029 --> 07:27.906
