07:27.906 --> 07:30.742
It'll never make
their problems go away.

07:31.534 --> 07:33.787
But I can.

07:33.787 --> 07:36.289
Now, no one's ever gonna
call me a hero,

07:36.289 --> 07:39.584
but I've come up with
a mutually beneficial solution

07:39.584 --> 07:41.711
for people like Caitlyn:

07:41.711 --> 07:47.050
get rid of their monsters
by giving mine what he needs.

