11:51.544 --> 11:53.379
You know what I mean, Chris.

11:53.379 --> 11:56.424
We got a stack of missing person
reports to follow up on.

11:57.800 --> 11:59.302
-Come on!

11:59.302 --> 12:00.970
-Holy shit, it's Teddy Lobo.
-What the fuck? Come on!

12:00.970 --> 12:03.097
-Are you sure?
-You know who I am?

12:03.097 --> 12:04.933
I'm Teddy fucking Lobo!

12:04.933 --> 12:06.434
