it makes you

16:01.544 --> 16:04.046
some sort of a monster.

16:04.046 --> 16:07.300
Do you have any idea
how inconsiderate that is?

16:07.300 --> 16:09.510
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

16:09.510 --> 16:14.307
My needs are the only thing
that matters, servant.

16:14.307 --> 16:16.309
